OL,3,CRoad safety fears raised due to extent
OL,4,Cof potholes
OL,6,FAn MP has raised road safety fears due
OL,7,Fto the extent of potholes on Northern
OL,8,FIreland's roads.
OL,10,FUpper Bann representative Carla
OL,11,FLockhart is calling for immediate
OL,12,Faction to fix the problem, as claims
OL,13,Ffor car repairs have run into millions
OL,14,Fof pounds.
OL,16,FMs Lockhart has told UTV she has
OL,17,Freceived hundreds of complaints about
OL,18,Fa number of roads.
