OL,3,CRoad safety fears raised due to extent
OL,4,Cof potholes
OL,6,F"The roads are horrendous, generally
OL,7,Facross Northern Ireland, and the
OL,8,Fweather has not been kind over the
OL,9,Flast couple of days," the DUP MP said.
OL,11,F"It has created a lot more potholes,
OL,12,Fbigger potholes, and cars are being
OL,13,Fdamaged left, right and center, and my
OL,14,Ffear is someone will be seriously
OL,15,Finjured."
OL,17,FThose fears are shared by a local
OL,18,Fbusinessman.
