OL,3,CRoad safety fears raised due to extent
OL,4,Cof potholes
OL,6,FShop owner Don Woolsey said: "I
OL,7,Fborrowed a couple or three cones off
OL,8,Fmy brother here and I went down to the
OL,9,Fmarks where the very poor road is.
OL,11,F"I was very concerned for the public
OL,12,Fin general that somebody was going to
OL,13,Fbe badly hurt or killed, and I've
OL,14,Fheard about a lot of people having
OL,15,Ftheir cars, their wheels and rims
OL,16,Fdamaged and certain things to their
OL,17,Fcars."
