OL,3,CRoad safety fears raised due to extent
OL,4,Cof potholes
OL,6,FIn 2024-25, a total of 4,696 road-
OL,7,Frelated claims were made to the
OL,8,FDepartment for Infrastructure, and as
OL,9,Fa result #7.9m has been paid out.
OL,11,FThat's an increase from around #3.5m
OL,12,Fwhich was paid out in 2020-21.
OL,14,FThe department insists it is committed
OL,15,Fto raising the standard of road
OL,16,Fmaintenance in the hope of reducing
OL,17,Flong-term costs and enhancing safety.
